text: Musino () is a rural locality (a village) in Novopetrovsky Selsoviet, Kugarchinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 103 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 11 km from Mrakovo, 4 km from Saitkulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kugarchinsky District
title: Musino, Kugarchinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
